\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We went to the public baths.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How often would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would that be a family outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh not all - we - we took it at different times, you know what I mean, but that was our practice - once a week to the public baths.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have clean clothes to put on after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Oh yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That was just once a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, that's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Whereabouts did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there any occasion when you'd eat in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, if we had company on a Sunday we had tea in the best room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did she have a range or did she have a gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Gas stove I believe - best part of my boyhood. Yes, she did - gas stove - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When was the breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Time? Seven thirty to eight a.m.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that the same for all of you or did your father have it earlier?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, father would be up - father would probably have it at quarter to six - five forty-five in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would he have to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
This is funny this is. Well I can't be truthful about that. Well, he would have what there was to eat according to financial resources. That's the best answer of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would he have when times were good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh he would have extras - eggs and bacon galore of course for breakfast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And if there wasn't very much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He'd probably have bread and marmalade, something like that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, we were all bought up the same, oh yes, there's no other way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have anything different on Sundays?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, if we were lucky we could have egg and bacon on a Sunday, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about your mid-day meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of thing would you have during the week for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, our mid-day meal - that was mother's work of art - let's put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would she make for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well it's so hard to describe that - she would probably go and buy sixpennyworth of meat pieces - and make 
soup, soup, soup. So we probably had some soup for three days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Anything else with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes. Then she'd carry on and make up the best under the purse, you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There wasn't any more meat at that meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no. We - we did not have meat every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How often in the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We may have meat two or three times a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would it be otherwise?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - you can say hot-pot, bread and cheese, a bit of bacon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about Sunday lunch?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh Sunday was special. We always had a baked - roast dinner on a Sunday and not less things were very bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother make her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Or her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about bottling fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, a city woman - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would she make pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember what she made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, pick - say pickled onions and piccalilli.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 She didn't make wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did she make beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they have an allotment - did they grow their own vegetables?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, my father had an allotment - yes. And that helped us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Locally where we lived you see. That - that's what helped us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 "hat would he grow - can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh everything that grows in a vegetable garden - every - I - I had an allotment myself you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That was later on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you help him when he had it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. I used to go out selling his produce.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where did you sell it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just your neighbours around the streets with a little barrow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He made enough for you and more then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He couldn't keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, we had no livestock - no. If we had livestock those days in London it was a few chickens in the backyard always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But you didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, we had no chickens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But you knew people around who did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh yes, the majority had livestock. Well, if you don't mind me mentioning this that the livestock those days was more tasty than any chicken you buy today - they were bro
ught up in the back yards in London and they were fattened up for Christmas - but you never tasted a chicken like it now. That is right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you ever have tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that because you couldn't get it or because it was expensive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well - I think the right answer is that mum and dad - were not with it as we would say now. In other words mum and dad were probably a bit prejudiced against tinned food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you wouldn't have tinned vegetables either?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There was no chance of extra meat such as a rabbit from poaching?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Rabbit - rabbit occasionally - yes, because they were cheap.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you get that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 At the butchers. Ostend rabbit was the one that we always used to have. Hot flavour - known as O
stend rabbits - they were wonderful. And they were very, very cheap.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There was no chance of getting any on the side from friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember seeing your mother keeping less food for herself at a meal so the rest of the family could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Definitely. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 "ho would she give more too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh she wouldn't sort it out at all. But she would - mother - mother's self was last - let's put it that way. Personally - mother - whatever was going mother was last to get it. We all came before mother - let's put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would she serve your father first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Dad first. Then us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Or vice versa - doesn't matter. Father would come first - definitely. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would he have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, definitely. Yes, oh, of course he would - so - he had to work for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you allowed to talk during meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. That's nice - I'm glad you asked that. My father had one word at the meal table. That word was silence. And if w
e disobeyed the word silence we were for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would happen to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well, the elder one, that would be me, I would be strapped and sent up to my - up to or down to bedroom, you know. And I knew I must not interrupt or speak during meal time. That was a very, very strict rule.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you ask for the salt to be passed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Anything reasonable like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you choose what you wanted to eat or did you have to eat what you were given?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, you eat what you were given or go without.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you had to eat it all up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Every time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If anything was left on your plate what did your parents say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Very annoyed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would you get strapped for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, but very annoyed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you ask for second helpings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, if it was there then you - we would get it if it was there.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you ask for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, our manners at the table had to be - perfect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you bring toys or a book to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When could you leave the table - did you have to ask?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Always had to ask to leave the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can I leave the table, mum?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would she always say yes or would she say wait until the end of the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh wait 'til - whatever - whatever the circumstances you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you all sit at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 All together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have the same places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your mother served it did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did she bring the serving dishes to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no - it would always be put onto the plate and brought in to you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was your mother an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did she show you affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of way would she do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Motherly way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If you had any worries could you share them with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember a time when you did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 W
ell I can quite twice really. Each time I was called to the services. You follow what I mean. Each time I was called to the - to the - Her Majesty's services.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was your father an easy person to talk to?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well moderately - yes. Not quite so easy as mum - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he show affection easily?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He was an affectionate father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If you had worries could you share them with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes. No difference - no. Good mum and dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they expect you to behave towards them in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Definitely - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of way would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 To highly respect them in every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they expect you to behave towards your sister in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, shall - shall I say to be correct towards my sister - to do it as it should be done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If you were hit by another child would your parents say you should hit the child back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Every time. No sympathy. Once we - once - once we were old enough you see within reason, you know what I mean do
n't you. Don't come here crying - look after your troubles yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What kind of person do you think your parents hoped you would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's a hard one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think they had a definite idea of what they wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I - I should - their idea was that I should grow up a reasonably decent citizen. I can't go much further than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were there certain things they thought were important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, behaviour - right or wrong - right and wrong - right and wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did they think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Unforbidden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your father wouldn't ever swear?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not at home - never. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When your parents were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Emphasise no. The strap again then. The strap again if we - if we joined in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If you did something they didn't like was it always the strap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, no. I'll quote - my time when I got to fourteen of being out of a night was ten o'clock. Dad says I want you in at ten o'clock. And when I started I disobeyed him one
 night. I was allowed to disobey once. And I done it again - and that was the last time I disobeyed. Because the disciplined. I was strapped and put to bed.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How many straps did he give you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Probably three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 After he'd done it how did he behave to you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Quite normal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No grudges?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it always your father - your mother didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, mother never touched us - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 She didn't punish you in any other way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you feel about it when you were punished - did you feel resentful?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well, I felt like the average child would feel. I'd feel very small which is obvious and at the time I would resent my - my father but after again I would be the same - I would forget all about it and knew I - knew I'd done wrong.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think you got your ideas about how to behave from both your parents or from one more than the other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, mum and dad both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When you had a birthday would it be a special day in the family - would it be different from any other day? Did you have presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - we - we would have presents according to financial resources.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What kind of thing - can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, very minor. Very minor things. The things - things that cost a few coppers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they got in the market as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have anything special to eat on birthdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No guests or friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No - I think my birthday is Christmas Day - I think I used to have a cake - it was called
 a Christmas cake and a birthday cake you see combined.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You didn't have guests in specially?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Relations. Nothing apart from relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What happened on Christmas Day - what did you do with your mother and father and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We never le
ft home - we always stayed at home. And - if we had relations the full entertainment was - just a happy sing-song between you, that's all I can say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have musical instruments to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, we - we had a piano all our life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who played it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 My sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, mother didn't play. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You'd sing carols at Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, and - and ordinary songs also. And songs - popular songs - of that day. Popular songs of that day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Special games for Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - no, just ordinary indoor games, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did anyone particularly sing in the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no particular singing - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you sing together as a family apart from Christmas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I should say no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your sister wouldn't play the piano and -?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh she may play the piano but we - we wouldn't have what we call a sing-song.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your parents play games with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Indoor games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things would they play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Cards, draughts, beat-your-neighbours - cut-of doors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things outside would they do? Would they play with you outside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, because we would be playing in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And your parents wouldn't go in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, a few. Nothing special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You can't remember any titles or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Only - only one I can remember we always carried Pears dictionary.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about newspapers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In the old days I think it was still functioning the Daily Herald - 'cos father was socialist - Daily Herald.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 John Bull. That's one I do remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother or father read a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just moderately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your mother more than your father or the other way round?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I'd say dad read the most.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he read aloud to the family - to your mother and sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, read aloud a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 To all of you together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If the subject suited the children only.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 From a newspaper or from books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, only if the subject suited the children would he read aloud.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother read aloud?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, she used to the same - the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember a funeral in the family before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What happened - who was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well, you want to know the details of the funeral? Well it was an aunt's and she were an Irish lady - born in Ireland and she was buried in her wedding dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you see her in the dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
And - yes, I saw - I can remember this as - one of the minor things - I can remember seeing my aunt in a coffin in her wedding dress and I - I should say I was about - seven or eight at that time, no more. I should be about seven or eight at that time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you feel about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What words shall I describe. I should say a little bit mysterious at that - at that age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You weren't frightened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I don't think so - no. And - being Irish it was - they have an Irish Wake if you've heard - ever heard of an Irish Wake - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you describe it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - everybody drinks a lot of beer and although the person dies everybody appears to enjoy }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 their self}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  tremendously.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 About how many?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, say a dozen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you had lots of relations living around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right. Uncles and aunts.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they all Irish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, some were born in Ireland and some were not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did people wear at the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Their best clothes. Always black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were the best clothes black anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, I - I should have said black. And they would try somehow to get black clothes for a funeral - don't ask me where the money came from but it was done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you taken out visiting neighbours by your mother when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Very occasionally. Relations - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 With your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Mum and dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you taken shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Occasionally - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you ever go out with just your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. I told you - before.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about Bank Holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Practically the same as any other day. Dad - mum and dad would take us probably to a fair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember one in particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I can.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Wanstead Flats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How old were you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Eleven or twelve I should say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember anything special there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, there's hardly any difference - that's one of the few things still the hooplas and the darts and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were there any exhibits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, well they was - the - the fat lady and - and a few freaks of nature you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go away for holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you spend Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Same as any other day.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But you weren't at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, weren't school - but apart from school - same as any other day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And did the polishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's it - we done - we both done our - we both helped mum in the house - put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 As children you didn't go off anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not unless it was to play in the street in the usual way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Sunday? Sunday school - without fail.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go to church in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Always Sunday school in the afternoon - always. No, we never went to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, we - mum and dad were not church goers so - but we were made to go to Sunday school always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long would that be - about an hour or two?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were your parents not churchgoers because they believed strongly about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Hundred per cent Christians but not churchgoers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go on any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Epping Forest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that often or just once a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, once a year outing really and truly - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Any other activities at all with the Sunday school - singing or -?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There was the usual activities - they formed little choirs, you know, and - and made their own entertainment, I'll put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there a temperance club attached to the Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Attached to the Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Or to the church that the Sunday school was attached to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, yes, definitely, yes, in the old days - yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you join that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Any other clubs attached to the church?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 Women\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  clubs - mother's meeting on a Monday. I remember that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it a Catholic church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, this one - this one was not a Catholic church, no, Church of England.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they say grace at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, we - we were taught - brought up to say prayers before went to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your mother taught you that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember what she taught you to say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The Lord's prayer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said your father was a socialist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Hundred per cent socialist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Why do you think he was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Conditions of living.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Had he always been a socialist or did he become one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, he was always socialist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So - the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember them voting before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother vote as soon as she could in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 As soon as she got the vote she - she used the vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So they were active?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In some places men risked losing their jobs if they voted differently from their employers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's quite right - they did - in the old days - that is true.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did that happen to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No. No, no. No. That hap - that happened more so in small industries. That did happen in small industries but not in your big - such as docking industry or railway - it wouldn't happen in the big industries you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was your father a member of the socialist party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, of the Labour party - yes. The Independent Labour Party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he work for it - did he go canvassing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But he was an official member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 A - a member.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And your mother as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, mother as well - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did she work for them at elections?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they take part in political activity apart from election time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So they were strong voters but they didn't join in the activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When they weren't working what did your father and mother do? Did they have any special hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well father's only hobby was gardening. Mother - I should say mother's work was mending all our clothes at different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That was work rather than leisure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 She didn't get much spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your father go out to a club in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, nothing like that at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And your mother never went out to enjoy herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, not apart from mum and dad - they wouldn't - everything was together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If they did go out together where would they go? To music hall?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I - I - there's only one 
place I can remember - that was the Queen's music hall, Popular. Very, very old established music hall. Very, very old - I can memorize this very well. Gracie Fields was there before she was ever discovered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go and hear her too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes, yes. I can remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The whole family would go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, occasionally. Occasionally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your father and mother sometimes went by themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who would stay with you when they did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just us two together - brother and sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And they wouldn't mind leaving you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your father wouldn't have played any sport or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, he was no sportsman - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he bet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he disapprove of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Never discussed it. He - he never gambled - he never gambled in any way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they belong to a savings club - you mentioned a club earlier on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I should - you can - no, didn't have enough to save, put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So there was no boot club or sick club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
He - yes, sick club, yes. Necessity. Sick club - a sick club probably at - a sick club probably at sixpence or ninepence a week and a clothing club to help to clothe us at probably the same figure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about a funeral club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Yes, we were all insured for death. That was regarded by mum and dad as a necessity - to give you a decent funeral. Very important - very important those days, very, very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you get on with your sister - did you get on well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Normally well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No quarrels?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Well, you know, the brother and sister usual, put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you play with your sister or did you play with neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Mostly played with boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And in the street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Anywhere else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In the park - occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That was quite near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, well - within a quarter of an hour say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things did you play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I can only say the usual children's games.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Nothing stands out in your mind particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well boys I suppose we used to call it coppers and robbers. In the old day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you play football?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. I played a fair amount of football - yes. Always played football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And you went to watch it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you allowed to play with anyone you pleased or did your parents feel strongly about some children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We were allowed to play with anyone we wished to providing they were O.K.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your mother and father say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well mum and dad knew all right whether they - who we was playing with and they knew what sort of children they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There were some children near you who they wouldn't want you to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - who they - who they would object to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of grounds would they be objecting on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Their behaviour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What their parents did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, their parents wouldn't come into it really and truly. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 
The child's be - the child's be - you can see the parents would be responsible for it if you like but - the child's behaviour wouldn't correspond with our behaviour shall I - I think that's the correct way.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you get dirty when you played - did your mother mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, no, didn't worry about that. No, we could get as dirty as we liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, no facilities.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Bicycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Cigarette cards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You had a good collection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, quite good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What happened to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh dear me, when I got older I probably gave them to the younger child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Any other hobbies you remember? You didn't have any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, we - we never - we had no pets when we were young whatsoever - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you take part in a football club at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, just used to play football generally you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go to any theatres or other concerts when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes - mother used to make an effort to take us to a pantomime once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That would be either the Borough Theatre Stratford which is East London
 - used to be called the Borough, I don't - I think it's a picture house now - or the Popular Hippodrome. No, you wouldn't know. Well, that's a pic - that might be a Bingo hall now, probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No cinemas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Occasionally, yes, occasionally. Occasion
ally, according to the - according to the financial resources governed everything you're talking about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Did anyone like a neighbour ever come in and help your mother for example - you don't remember when she was having the baby but do you know about what happened then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No we - I can - I describe it this way - mother was well liked and she always got on well with neighbours and they were very helpful.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If they could help anyone out the would?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, very good - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember a time when that happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I should only say during sickness. During sickness or death. I should say. During sickness or death.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There were lots of relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Quite a number - yes. Father's relatives.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you see them often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Pretty often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would they come to your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Occasionally. Vice versa - yes - occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they large families or were they like your own? Did they have the same kind of households?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, more or less the same. The same. The same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your parents have friends around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 A few. Just say a few - not a lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they have the same friends - did your father have friends and your mother have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, all the same - no, not separate at all. No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He wouldn't see his working friends in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they invited into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, occasionally.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 About how often do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Depend on the type of friend I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would they be offered a meal or a drink when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, it wouldn't permit it I don't think. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 It was the same friends, it wasn't your father's or your mother's friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would the ever drop in without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Not as I knows of - no. Wasn't done in our - in our - in our way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And your parents wouldn't go and drop in on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 One often hears that they made their own amusements in those days - can you remember anything your parents would do with their f
riends or relatives when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I should say mostly talk politics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I was thinking of singing or that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh well - you - yes, well that would be normally - yes - join in and make mu - in other words you'd make your own 
amusements. You'd make your own amusement regarding - a sing-song - somebody would play the piano, you'd all join in singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would they play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 occasionally}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  you'd play cards - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would they play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I can't think of any other games - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 People divide society into different social classes and groups.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In that period up until 1918 did you think of people in that way of belonging to one group or another group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did I - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you tell me what distinguished the groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The things that distinguished the groups which your financial bearing. Just that. The financial bearing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think there were two groups or many groups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There were three groups actually. Sh
all we say you had the labour group - well, say there's three groups - you had the labour group - you had the middle classes - and you had - if you like to say - the rich. But then you had another group that always imagined they were middle class, if you 
know that group. They weren't middle class - they were working class truthfully but the man may be getting another two shillings a week more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would he have a different kind of job the people of that class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He'd probably be a white collar worker. 
Yes. He'd probably be - be a pen worker - because in those days the - we don't know why but the pen worker always - always thought himself superior to the manual worker.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Which of the groups did you belong to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You wouldn't make any divisions among the working men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No. They were one group. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of people besides your father's colleagues belonged to that group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I can only say the majority of people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Mostly dockers - in that part of London. Mostly - dock - docks - something }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 appertaining}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  to docks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you bought up to treat the people in the different groups in different ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. We were brought up to treat everyone alike.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Even if they had more money than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, oh yes, yes. Yes. We learnt that - what I'm referring to now we learnt ourselves as we got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You weren't taught to touch your cap to anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, we were - oh yes we were - we - I was always taught to rais
e my hat to a lady irrespective of who she was - a female. It doesn't matter who she was - whether she was next door neighbour or Lady Jane Grey - I was taught to raise my hat to the ladies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not to a boss or if you met a teacher?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, but we were
 still brought up to used the word Sir. The same - the same way as - as - as raising your hat to a lady - or in a different way really. You - you - we were brought up to Sir our employer - well that was stupid really because we was only brought up to Sir 
him - Sir him because we were under obligation to him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there anyone who lived hear you that you called Sir? Or Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember anyone calling your father or mother Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Or touching their hats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Mr and Mrs Mahony.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who were the most important people in the area that you lived in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
The most important people. I think you'll laugh what I'm going to say probably. Well I should say the publicans were one of the most important.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Why were they important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - one of the reasons why they were so important because they gave so much pleasure to so many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They always treated everyone equally?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, business. But the reason - the reason being that - their product was cheap and they gave so many so much pleasure.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you come in contact with them when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. With these people - no, not at all. Not until I drunk beer myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How old were you when you started that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, when I started that - as soon as I went in the services which is obvious - seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not before then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, not before I was seventeen I never tasted beer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You wouldn't be sent to the pub to get some for your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, occasionally - yes, I'd be sent round with a bottle or a jug to get a pint of porter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did they treat you when you went in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, as a customer. But with respect - with respect - as a customer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did the other customers smile to see a boy coming in or was it common?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh no, no, no. It was just general. Oh no. The majority of children used to go out with a jug and get mum a pint of beer or half a pint of beer whatever it might be. According to finances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They wouldn't drink any themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, no. Accordin
g to the finances - if they - if they was wealthy they'd have a pint and if they wasn't wealthy they'd have a half a pint you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who would the shopkeepers associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Now - listen to this little bit - now the majority shopkeepers in those
 days was very good - reason being you were a customer and part of your life you lived on tick You know what I mean by that? Now, you lived on credit so through living on credit you were highly respected because you owed them money. Now -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They couldn't afford to lose you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Correct - they couldn't afford to lose you. No. I - I quote for you if I may. During the big dock strike my father was on strike from the docks for probably three months and mother had no money coming in whatsoever - after the l
ast weeks wage she got. And I think he got a few shillings a week strike pay, in those days, it might have been ten shillings but it couldn't have been any more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember what year this was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - I'm quoting before the first world war n
ow so we'll say 1912 and '13. Why I was quoting was that my father was on a big dock strike. We're talking about shopkeepers. Well there was no money coming into the house and if it wasn't for our grocer we would have definitely starved.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They supported the strike then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Yes. If it wasn't for our grocer we - would have starved. Now our grocer give my mum and dad credit for over three months. But every bit of food we had for four of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long did it take you to pay that off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Now I coul
dn't tell you that but I could tell you one thing - every farthing was paid back. Every farthing was paid back. I don't know how much it was it doesn't what mum and dad went short of afterwards - every farthing was paid back.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who do you think were friends with the shopkeepers - would they mix with themselves or who do you think they mixed with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well the competition was so keen they would mostly mix with the customers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What about clergymen - who would they mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Now that's a bit ha
rd because - I was - although I wasn't brought up as a Catholic my family was Catholic. The area I lived in when I was a boy - that was a Catholic majority - it still is in fact now. Catholic were more powerful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Could you tell me your exact address in Poplar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, Tetley Street. Can't - I couldn't tell you the number. Tetley Street. A very - a poor neighbourhood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When you went to West Ham where did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Beckton Road. Beckton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said your mother worked as a factory hand after your father died and do you know exactly what she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, she worked at the Lampson Paragon works - papercraft. Making paper bags. Helping to - helping to make paper bags.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You mentioned that as a boy you used to polish the brasses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your sister have a job of her own to do as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I think - I'd say to help generally in the housework that would be correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There wouldn't be anything particular?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, to help generally - to help mother generally 
in the housework. We both done that but that was my special job regarding cleaning the brasses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said that your father got up earlier than the rest of you and what he had for breakfast - but who got his breakfast for him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 For mid-day meals you said you had soup and then hot-pot or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Mid-day meal was our dinner and - the only meal after that was our tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What time would you have that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That would be round five thirty. And we'd probably - be allowed a slice of bread and jam before going to bed or something like that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would you have anything to drink with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 A cup of cocoa.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it different on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I should say mum and dad used to make an effort to have a roast dinner on Sunday. Mid-day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have anything different in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We'd go just the same. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 
If we had - if we were entertaining - we had friends or relatives we - we would have what you call a high tea. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We - in other words a bit of cake with it probably.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Nothing cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said your parents were against tinned things - did they ever buy dried vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no. When I was a boy - I think I can safely say there was no such thing. There was no such thing. And we had no 
cause to be - as I told you, my dad ran an allotment so we - he - we - he saved money by growing all our own vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He was able to grow all of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, all our vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You never had to buy any extra?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember where your sister sat when she was very little before she could feed herself at the meal table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I should say in a high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember that clearly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Fairly clearly because there's only three years between us - two and a 
half years between us. But - yes I should - yes, I'm almost sure in a high chair because it was about the house for years after.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 On Sundays did you have special clothes when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We had what they termed a best suit. And a best dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that kept for Sundays only?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Sundays and high days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of high days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - if you had relatives coming or holiday - Christmas - Easter Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 On Sunday did you play games or did your parents think it was wrong to play on Sundays - or work on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We occasionally played games - no, my parents didn't think it was wrong - they were not narrow minded in - in any direction whatsoever.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said your father was a member of the Independent Labour Party - do you remember the party he voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, the Labour party.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember the name of the candidate he voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, Mr William Thorne.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What was the constituency?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 West Ham - South. Now - it is now - this is after we left Poplar
 I'm referring to - I was about - I was getting on for fourteen then. That was the County Borough West Ham, now it's been re-named New Ham.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When you were still living in Poplar can you remember who he voted for then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Labour. But I - oh, George Lansbury. Oh dear me, yes, I couldn't forget that. Impossible. Poor old George Lansbury - lovely man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember anything they said about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Said about who - George Lansbury? Well, he was - he was - he was just an idol to the working cla
ss. He was on a pedestal. All his life. He was a real - he was a real worker for the working class people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember anything about the issue when he resigned in 1912?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I can't remember nothing about that really at all - no, no. No, I c
an't remember. Did he resign 1912 for something? Yes, yes, I re - I just got a - now you've brought that up you know, that's just rung a bell, you know what I mean don't you? But I - I can't - just couldn't tell you anything about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember anything he did in Poplar which he was talked about for particularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, I can't remember anything outstand - I can only remember - it's so obvious he must have been a good man because everybody irrespective of party was highly respected - highly respected. And you could say he was loved by the - working class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your parents go to political meetings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, they - they would only go to political meetings - probably at election times - election times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But apart from that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They just voted and talked about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What time did your father get in from work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Ah - now - you want this just - just that question answered or - sort of details you know. Right. Well, my father'd get home fro
m work - as late as he could to be truthful - to get more money. His time was from seven in the morning 'til five in the evening but if he could do overtime he would do overtime. Because the docks those days the majority of the men were casual workers - a
n
d they used - what they called stand on the stones - that's on the pavement - every morning and wait for the foreman to point to them and take them on for the days work. That's well there's one word for all that - was racket, you see. That was the answer 
to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So if he got work he'd stay on as long as he could?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
He would stay on - he would stay on only as long - until it - the time it took to load the boat. You see, a stevedore loads the ship - a docker unloads the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696  ship}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 . My father was a stevedo
re. So - if - if the boat took fourteen days to unload in those days he would have fourteen days work and then - or if it took seven days - then he would almost be like looking for another job and start again. That was the routine. Although he was a steve
dore all his life - highly skilled stevedore, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So once he got hired for one ship he'd have work every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 He'd work every day until that ship was loaded. He would be on that - on that gang shall we call it, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Have you any idea what he got paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh, no - now, no, I couldn't tell you. Of course, I mean, when we talk now you say the wages were ridiculously low you see, well I just said to you that father used to struggle to get every hours overtime he could to make
 his money up so that would more or less tell you. I mean, of course, dockers and stevedores, all those men, when you compare in comparison they're millionaires now. It - it - it - thank god it's all happened - I mean progress you see. I - I mean as I sai
d to you before when people talk about good old days you - I feel like going off the deep end, you know what I mean don't you.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your father ever go to a pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes, my father - my father drunk beer moderately - moderately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he ever describe to you what went on in the pub?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I shouldn't say - no. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he go regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, no. He wasn't a regular at a pub - no. He - he would have a glass of beer, let's be truthful, when he could afford it. That is the basic of it all. When you could afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you know how often a week or a month that would be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I should say two or three times a week probably - roughly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said there were some children your parents didn't like you to play with when you were small because they didn't behave properly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh yes. I can only say this - that - that - mum and dad was like this. If they were very inferior, I think that's the right word, mum and dad didn't like us mixing with 'em. For example, if they knew t
he child was a thief we were not allowed to have anything to do with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember such a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, no, no, no. My memory - no. But that is what I mean. For example, if the child was a thief mum and dad would not allow us to have anything to do with the child or if the child was, shall I say bad, that's the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 word}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Have you any idea what sort of homes those children would have come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, there's one answer to that - they - they wouldn't have come from no poorer home than I 
come from but they would have come from a far inferior home. But financially they would have come from a home no poorer, but shall I say, educationally much inferior.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you mean the parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right. That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They would have had a different education or a different attitude?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 A different attitude - how can I put it. Shall I say they were as much interested in the word wrong as they were in the word right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would those sort of parents do different kinds of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh no. Different kinds of work? Oh no, no, no. You got them - those in every walk of life in the working class the same as you - you have the good and bad in every other walk of life. You see. I mean it doesn't signify a lot - a lot of people ca
n have a load of money and they can still be bad. See?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When you were a child at school did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, nothing at all. No, no, nothing at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go for walks when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, the only thing - we went for walks occasionally with mum and dad at the week-ends. Shall I say that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where would you go then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 To a park mostly - to a park - to a park.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You told me you sometimes went to cinemas if you had the money to go? Did you prefe
r cinemas to music hall or did you feel cinemas were less interesting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, our family - no, no, we liked the old music hall - preferred the old music hall best, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Whereabouts was the nearest cinema?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, not far. Eastern Dock Road, Poplar. And the nearest music hall High Street Poplar.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was the cinema a going concern?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh yes. Yes, they - because they hadn't been running all those years when I was a boy, you know what I mean don't you. They were a going concern - and the music hall were going concerns. Of course, you see, it only cost you sixpence to get in the gallery.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How much would the cinema be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No more. Probably less. On a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  matinee - may only be threepence on a children matinee. Probably less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of films did they have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well, I should say - the same as today practically. The same type of films you see, they're showing films on television which are twenty years old aren't they very often. And they were still very, very good some of t
hem then you - well you know that yourself if you've seen some of them. You see, they're still very, very good some of those were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In the very early days before the first war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Before the first world war - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they silent films?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Silent? Oh yes, certainly - silent films, oh yes - definitely. Silent films - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there a pianist who played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Pianist - oh yes, the piano all the time the pictures were on. And then as the time - as the years developed just before t
alkies came out the big cinemas had the organ, you see, mostly organ then. That was just prior to the - prior to the talkies coming out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That was later on after the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You said some of your parents were invited into the house as guests - which ones were invited in - what was special about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - I can only say they were close friends who mum and dad had confidence in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they political friends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not necessarily. Not necessarily - no. No. Not necessarily.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would they be friends from your father's work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Occasionally - yes, yes, some - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where would your mother's friends come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Neighbours. Mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember who the school teachers would be friendly with and who they'd know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I can't give you much information about school teachers except from being our teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your teachers live around Poplar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I should say they travelled - travelled into the school myself. But I'm not su
re about that. I'm not sure about that. You see, even teachers weren't highly paid - that's what you have to think of. They couldn't afford to travel far, that's obvious.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How about the employers and managers - did they live around there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Now - the employees of what - businesses do you mean or - factories do you mean? Oh no - that's obvious. That's obvious.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Whereabouts would the bosses of that area have lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Of that area - well, I should say the majority would live - would have lived 
at Woodford in Essex. You see, there was no moneyed people lived in Poplar. The only moneyed people were the business people, shall I say shopkeepers. The - the comfortable shopkeepers I mean - not all. But there was no moneyed people lived in Poplar - it
 was just a very, very thick industrial working class area. And - the number one labour was the docks. Nine men out of every ton worked in the docks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you wouldn't have formed any idea who the employers knew and what their social life was when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, the only thing is this - I can say this without contradiction. The employers were separate from the subject we're on entirely. They were no part of the working class. They were no part except for paying them their wages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You wouldn't come across them in any other way at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No other way whatsoever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How about the clergymen - was there any problem in the area about different religions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I lived in a very, very strong Catholic area, I told you that. And - the on
ly thing I can say that the Catholic Father's was highly respected. But I was too young to know much about it, you know what I mean don't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But there was no problem between the few Anglicans or Protestants there }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7762104\charrsid7228696 
might}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  have been there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, 
there was no religious - oh no, no, we had none of that whatsoever. No, we had none of that. Catholics and Protestants got on all right together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 It wasn't a Catholic Sunday school you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No. Well to - to give you an example my father 
- this will show how well they got on together - my father was a Catholic and my mother was a Protestant. So that will give you a little idea that there was really and truly very little bad feeling - or no bad feeling shall I say.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And his relations wouldn't worry about her being Protestant?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, no. Well they may have worried a little bit - grandmother - she was a little bit prehistoric - probably she did think dad was wrong in marrying a Protestant, which is, shall I say, it's a little bit natur
al for them - at that - at that age, I mean - at that time you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Had she come from Ireland?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 My grandmother - yes. My - my father's mother come from Ireland - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Had your grandfather come from Ireland?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they come to England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 During their life sometime but I don't know when.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You don't know if it was before your parents were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no. No. Well they - they came to England after I was born. Yes, after I was born. Definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your grandfather work in England?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, the latter part of his life. In the docks also.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What had he been in Ireland?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No idea, love. No idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember any other Protestants in the neighbourhood at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well my memory won't allow that. But we knew many Protestants, put it that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of people - did you know any Non-conformists?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I should say - yes, definitely, among our friends - yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were they different kinds of people at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well we didn't cla
ss them different at all. They were - they were in the same working position as ourselves irrespective of their religion.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They didn't have different characters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were there any different standards of living among the working people at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well - yes, I - I think - I think I'm wrong what I'm going to say - but in the days we're referring to the white collar worker was looked upon as something higher than the factory or the dock worker was. He wasn't - oh no, he wasn't at all
. But - he went out to work as smart as he possibly go to work to the office every morning and - and also he thought he was better. See. He thought he was better than the man who worked in the factory or worked in the dock - see. But of course it - it did
n
't work out at all as you know. He was no better - he was no different - he was just a working man again. Very lowly paid. Probably he received less than the docker or the factory worker did. But he always thought himself on a higher level than the docker
 or the factory worker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was his way of life different - did he try to live in a slightly different way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, he - I think - the true way to describe it is - he tried to live above his means.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In what sort of way - the kind of food or they way he furnished his house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I should say - he lived in the way that he incurred far more debt than the factory worker or the dock worker would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there any difference between the factory worker and the dock worker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh - no - they - they
 were more - they were on the same level - those two. Now the factory worker and the dock worker were practically on the same level. But the office worker was on another level altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 There were no groups among the factory workers and dock workers who were lower than most of the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
No, I - no the way you should - no, the correct way - is there any groups who were higher. Now that is the correct way. Yes, there were groups that were higher. Those that held the higher positions. In the place of business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would this be the foremen and the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 charge hands}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - managers. Supervisors. Those who run the business.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would their families live a slightly different way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, of course they would - that is - that is obvious.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Are you talking about the people who were slightly higher among the working men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Yes. They're still working men. Well, I still regard it was working class. But they held - they held higher positions therefore their wages was much higher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you think of any groups as being rough and others respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well - I can only say that where I lived was same as any other neighbourhood - it had its rough streets and it had its quieter streets. No different to any other neighbourhood whe
re you go. There - there's more or less a rough quarter. No, that's the only way I can describe that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did both your mother and father have the same attitude towards the classes of people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Mother and father were almost the same. I should say identical in their outlook.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a special group?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh - no, not at all. No, no, no. Not in any way - no. No, no, no. No superior complex you mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not necessarily superior - just an idea of what group she belonged to in life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - it - she knew she belonged to the working class group. That's the only -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your father felt the same? Do you remember anyone being described as a real gentleman or a real lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well George Lansbury wa
s one. M.P. for Poplar - he was a real gentleman. Ladies I can't remember much about. And I - I can just slightly memorize two or three clergymen. Yes. Yes, they - they were regarded gentlemen because they made you feel at home. They never adopted a super
ior attitude that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there anything about the way they dressed or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, if they were clergymen they were always dressed in their - in their uniform, you know what I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember seeing a policeman round when you were a child?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh I should say so - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you think of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Very superior. In other words we had to be very careful.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you ever told when you were naughty 'I'll call a policeman'?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, that was a saying of mum and dad - yes, that - that's correct. That was one of the old fashioned sayings that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think they meant it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. 'Course not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You thought so then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 We - oh as a child we thought so then - yes, correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You don't remember any incidents when anybody you knew was in trouble with the police?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I'm afraid I don't memorize anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they treat people in any particular way do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, as a child I wouldn't - I couldn't quote fairly how the police were towards the police as a child - I couldn't quote that at all.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How about when you were in your teens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 But it's different now. Well, you still had to mind your p's and q's when the police were about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was your home rented?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you see anything of your landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I should say yes - occasionally we did see our landlord - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you feel about him as a landlord? Was he a good one - did he do the repairs and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, for those times they 
were moderately good. Yes, moderately good for those times - yes. Yes. Where - where I lived those times they were moderately good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did your parents feel when the time came to collect the rent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did my parents feel about it? They never fe
lt about it at all. They had - their attitude was it was a necessity. They had to pay for their shelter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They didn't feel the rents were too high?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, not where we lived - no, not then - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember your parents struggling to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes. All - all my childhood life - my parents had a struggle to make ends meet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you as a child feel about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, as I got older - I suppose the word I should use - I felt very bitter about it. When I saw there's
 so much around the world just the reverse. And my father had to work very, very hard for his living.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How old were you when you began to see things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Thirteen or fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What difference did it make to the family when your father was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Every difference. For the simple reason there was no money coming in. The firm never paid for illness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You were members of a sick club I think you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, a necessity. Father belonged to a sick club for necessity - he had to. 
And excuse me - the time I'm talking of if father was ill the doctors bills bad to be paid. There was no State Insurance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was he ill often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember a particular time - if he had any accidents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, he - he had an accident on board ship just before he died. And that accident hastened his death.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What was that - did something drop on him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - something like that. I can't memorize it but as you say probably something dropped on him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember what the doctor had to be paid for something like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, I couldn't - I'm sorry - no. No - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you know if they made any special allowance for people who were less well off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Who made? Oh no, no, no, no, no. The doctor - would 
charge - personally what he thought you could afford. Now that - that is the true answer. The average doctor. Because - he knew - the doctor knew if he would overcharge you he wouldn't get the money - so there - so there was no object in it at all. He kne
w he wouldn't get the money if he overcharged you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you ever get any help from a charity or from the Guardians of the Parish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Never. No, my mum and dad they were - shall I say }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 old-fashioned}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 . They wouldn't entertain it in any way. Doesn't matter what trouble they had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not even after your father died?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, mother went up to work. No, she still got no help - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were there any particular Irish clubs or organization in that area?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. But we belonged to none of them. There were several Irish clubs in Poplar because there was a lot of Irish people lived there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I - I don't know at all because we had no connection with them you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If there were people in that part of the world w
ho the other people disapproved of was there any special way in which the other families would show it? In some parts people would make rough music in this situation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember anything like that around your part?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well - ev
en the decent living poor people would object to being annoyed. Put it that way. Not that they could do anything about it probably but they strongly object to being annoyed.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What kinds of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well what you were describing just now - a noise - unnecessary noise - that sort of thing. Hooliganism.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If people behave in a way that other people felt bad would they take it into their own hands to do something about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I don't think so, no. No, they wouldn't the - intelligence for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your parents ever give you any lessons at all before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I should say no except A.B.C.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They saw you knew your letters before you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, the only - the only - the only tuition we probably had was to learn your alphabet and write your own-name and address.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go for the whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I can't memorize that - but at five I think you went for the whole day. I can't - I'm not sure about i
t but at five - under five - part day. But at five I think you went for the whole day. Five was the correct age for starting school when I was young - that was the correct age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What kind of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just an ordinary council elementary school. No, not a church school - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it mixed school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, boys and girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 Shanks}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  pony - walking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Fifteen minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go by yourself when you were very small or did }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 someone}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Probably mother took - probably mother took us at the beginning but when we knew the way we went by ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where did you have your mid-day meal - did you stay at school or go home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you think of school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, mid-day meals then at school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not for anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Not when I - not when you're talking about the age - no. No, no such thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you think of school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Personally I think I just treated it as a necessity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you feel about the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Some appealing and some not appealing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of reasons would they appeal for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Their personality. Their behaviour towards children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 If some were strict you didn't like them you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That - yes - that - but some were, shall I say, extreme strict.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things did they emphasise as important - for example manners or tidiness or punctuality.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Punctuality - yes, that was general naturally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Were you punished if you were late?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I think yes, not - not the first time but after a warning yes, we did have - get punished.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they feel strongly about speaking in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not all that amount no. No, no, not then - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did they punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it the same for the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I can't help you there - I can't - no I wouldn't commit myself on that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What else would you get punished for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Swearing. - in school. And doing - doing anything extremely wrong - got the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of things extremely wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well too much disobedience - too much disobedience.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Reasonable. Reasonable.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of way would they do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, they was always 
interested when it came round to examination time. They were obviously pleased if we - if we were up in the higher part of the class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they ask you what you did at school during the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they visit the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, occasionally. Yes, they used to go and visit the school - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would there be a special time when they would go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, a special time for parents to visit schools, yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And they met the teachers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Met the teachers - that's cor - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did he other children come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Yes. Yes, yes. All working class children at the school I went to, yes, definitely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did the teachers single out some children for special treatment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I should say myself yes that's human nature. That's the answer to that. Let's put it this way, there's always blue eyes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember any child that had blue eyes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, not off my memory - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did they have gangs among the schoolchildren?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, they all - they always had that - they always had that - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember being part of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I can't memorise - no, I don't think I was part of a gang - no. No, I wasn't part of a gang.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there children who were left out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Yes, you always had the child who was left out. Oh yes. The child who was left out would always be the one who was extremely backward in coming forward.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That wasn't you though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, I tried to hold my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you go to another school after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What age did you change?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I should say twelve - roughly. Council school just the same - yes. In a - in an in an industrial area just the same - West Ham.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that just boys or was it mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Boys and girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How far away was that from where you lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 About fifteen minutes from where we lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was it two schools near each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no, no. The first school we were talking about was at Popular and the second school we're talking about is when we moved to West Ham.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you walked to school again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Each time - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have your mid-day meal at home again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Home - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you feel about the second school - did you like that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Much of a muchness - about the same?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just the same - fifty-fifty. Nothing - nothing outstanding - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And they felt the same way about what was important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - they - they were just the same exactly. Exactly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Fourteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Probably. Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was there a chance to have part time education after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I think - I think I could ha
ve gone to evening classes. But I'm only surmising this - I'm not sure about this - but I think I could have gone to evening classes provided by the council - local authorities you see. But I never did go. I never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Why do you feel so strongly that you would have stayed on if you'd had the chance?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I've only thought that later years - not then I didn't think it because I thought it would have been to my advantage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 In getting a different job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. And in education generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you have any regrets about your education apart from this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Well, I'm satisfied now - got to be fair about this - I've got to Thank God for a lot. My number one in life is good health. No, I have no regrets - no regrets at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think you benefited from going to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Oh yes. Oh yes. Yes. That's a true answer. Well in - the obvious answer I mean - you don't necessarily go to school to grow up brilliant but I think to be truthful it gives you a lot more common sense than you woul
d have had if you hadn't gone to school. I think that's correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 While you were still at school did you have a part time job to make some money for yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, at the later stages I was - helping a newspaperman. That's all I can tell you on that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you remember how you got it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 By just going to the shop and asking the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 guv'nor}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  if he wanted a boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you have to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Deliver newspapers - to the houses where the people lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Was that in the morning and afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, only morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Not the evening paper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What hours did you work then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh, probably from - from half past seven to quarter to nine I should say roughly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 At weekends as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What were you paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh dear me - you're asking me something now aren't you. I should - I should say five shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You don't remember exactly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Wouldn't be no more - if it's as much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you give any of it to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh yes, definitely. Definitely. Probably gave mother four shillings out the five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would she spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The home. The house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you get on with your employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Reasonably - just accepted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you like doing it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Quite happy. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did it alter your attitude to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No, I don't think so, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You only had that one part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right - that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What was your first full time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well that was in a factory in th
e City. You want to know the details of it? Yes. Well I had about - three quarters of an hour tram ride to work and three quarters of an hours ride home and the first job was at perforated music company - we used to make music rolls for the pianolas, you 
know what I mean. I was on packing. And my wages were eight shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long were you in that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh - I should say twelve months roughly on that one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You were fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Fourteen - that's right - fourteen. Yes, that's right. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes. Seven shillings out of eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I think it was through an advert - newspaper. Best of my - best of my memory.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you remember how you got on with your colleagues?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 My colleagues - O.K.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How about the boss?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Never remember seeing him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 At that age I suppose I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Why did you leave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 To better myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you go onto after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I went into food distributing trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you do for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I was a warehouseman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Where was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 West Ham.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How much did you get then - do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I think I jumped to - to twelve shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long did you have that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I - I worked for that firm until I joined the services.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And you were seventeen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's it. I was between seventeen and eighteen then. Just over seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 So you were there about two and a half years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you have holidays on that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Now let's - now let's just think this out. The latter part of my service we got a weeks annual holiday. Not at the beginning - there was no holiday but the latter part of my service we got a weeks a
nnual holiday. In the food distributing. That was up to the time I went in the services - on me - on a plane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you work on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 All day Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. Lunch time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you work Saturdays in your first job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Any holidays at all in that one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You went into the services at seventeen and that would take us through to the end of that period wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's it - just over seventeen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What year were you demobbed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I - I was actually demobbed 1918 when the armistice was signed but I worked on to the Air Ministry for another year as a civilian.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 For how many years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, I was in seventeen - the armistice was November 1918 - well say two years - just over two year I done in the service actually.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you do for them when you stayed on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I was a telephone operator.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That take us up to the end of 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That brings it up - that brings it to the end of 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you do after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I went back to the food distributing trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 The same job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, the same firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 They kept it open for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How long did you stay with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Forty-five year. That's right - that's correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Until retiring?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes - that's when - up to when I retired - that's quite right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you keep the same job with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh I moved around on various jobs in the trade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Can you tell me what they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 My last job was? Well, I started from a
 - more or less a tea boy if you like and I finished up - being responsible for all the goods leaving the premises, up to a point. I was what they termed dispatch checker, you see. Responsible for all the firms goods going out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Would you have preferred to have done something else - a different kind of job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I should have done - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would you have liked to have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I'd have liked to have kept in the service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 And been a professional?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Airman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 For what reason?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well, there's only one word I think - security.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Didn't you feel secure in the job you had?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Those days - correct. Correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What did you feel could happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13063816\charrsid7228696 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696  - where are we - where have we got to - where have we actuall
y got to - 19 what - we got to the end of the first world war didn't we. Well, we got up to 1919. Now - from 1919 until the last great war things improved very little for the working class - over those number of years you see. So therefore things were pra
c
tically the same - how can I explain it - oh, the labour market was flooded. The majority of the time we had two million unemployed in this country. And my employer would not listen to the word increase in wages because he could afford to adopt that attit
u
de. And if I went to him and ask him for a rise - he would say to me - see all those names in that book - they want to come and do your job for ten shillings less than you're doing it. And that was the answer I got. But that - this - what I'm quoting now 
is not only me. I'm quoting generally because the capitalist had everything to his advantage - he had two million unemployed to play on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you feel this before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Oh no. Not - I didn't feel that - no, I didn't have those feeli
ngs before the first world war because - I hadn't had enough experience - I didn't know the meaning of the word want really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you belong to a union before the first war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Before the first world war? No. Because my firm then was a non-union firm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Does that mean you couldn't join the union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I couldn't join.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What would happen if you had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Probably got the sack.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you feel the workers had different interests from employers at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Workers had different interests from the employers? Oh yes, obviously.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You felt that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 
Yes, oh yes. No well the firm - the firm I worked for those days was a non-union firm. In - in other words it had no respect for unions. And - if I'd have been determined or they - if they'd have know that I held a union card I would have got the sack.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you feel there was a division of interest between the workers themselves? Between trained craftsmen and other workers at that time?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I think it's fairly logical that the u
ntrained craftsman would be a bit jealous of the trained craftsman. I think that's the right way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you feel then that you wished you'd had a training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes, I wish I'd have had a trade - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You didn't have an apprenticeship at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Do you think your full time job changed your general attitude to life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Definitely as time went on - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 When you first began - did you feel it then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, it took me longer than that. Say when I arrived at the age of - when I
 went into the services I was much wiser - that's the right way to put it. I was much wiser.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 What sort of ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Well I - I saw through my own eyes - the - the vast difference between the people who had a lot of money and the people who barely ha
d enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 You wouldn't have seen when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 That's correct.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you continue to live at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did working change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 How about your sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Your parents didn't treat you in any different way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 No, no. Both the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you spend your Sunday any differently - did you carry on going to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I don't think I went to Sunday school much after I was fifteen. But I was allowed to think for myself then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 I was beginning to at that age - I was beginning to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Did you feel the same way as your parents or differently?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9196494 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Hundred per cent the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3750637 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13587313\charrsid7228696 Why do you think you felt the same?
